<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="work-n">work <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /wɜːk/    美 /wɜːrk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>工作；劳动：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Though I had a lot of experience and a Master’s degree, I could not find satisfying work.
虽然我有丰富的经验和硕士学位，但我没能找到满意的工作。</p><footer>2012 全国</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She earned excellent grades through <strong>hard work</strong>. 
她通过艰苦的努力取得了优异的成绩。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>工作成果；产品：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Every designer hopes that his work can stand the test of time. 
每位设计师都希望自己的产品能经得起时间的考验。</p><footer>2012 上海</footer></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>著作；作品：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No matter how frequently performed, the works of Beethoven still attract people all over the world.
不管多么频繁地被演奏，贝多芬的作品依旧吸引着全世界的人们。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>工厂：工程：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a steel works 
钢铁厂</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Public works
公共/市政工程</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-work">at work</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在工作；在运转；有某种影响；起某种作用；</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was at work when I got a phone call. 
我工作时接到一个电话。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The machine is at work. 
这台机器正在运转。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When she came over to my house with her red eyes, I knew there were deeper issues at work.
当她红着眼睛来到我家时，我知道这里有更深层次的问题。</p></div>

<h3 id="out-of-work">out of work</h3>
<p>1.<strong>失业 (unemployed)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was worried about whether I would be out of work.
我担心自己是否会丢掉工作。</p></div></div>